


==================== QUICK LEARNER, how to become? =========================

01. Not afraid to say “I don’t know”

02. Identify and Focus on the most important things. How?
          -(Using Italian economist, the Pareto principle of 20/80. "Focus on the most important things that will give you the best results.")      
             Example:
              -Learning English/Spanish
              -Instead of trying to master every single grammar rule and vocabulary word, 
              -Identify and Focus on the 20% most commonly used grammar structures and vocabulary. It will help me to understand and communicate effectively in 80% of situations.
03. Set tight deadlines (Using British naval, Parkinson's Law "Work expands to fill the time available for its completion.")       
        -সহজ কথায়, 
          -একটি কাজের জন্য যত বেশি সময় বরাদ্দ করবেন, 
          -এটি শেষ করতে তত বেশি সময় লাগবে।

04. Capable of visualization (creating mental images or pictures in my mind)
05. Understand

06. Simplifying/Explain Capacity. "If you can not explain it simply, you don't understand it well enough" -Einstein's Philosophy on Explanation 
07. Can seek the opinions of experts.


-----



08. Know how to anticipate the future (mitigation and adaptation)        
09. Understand that many questions have no answer








